---
title: Tex Mex Lentil and Beyond Meat® Tortilla Soup with Peppers and Corn
description: Imagine all the flavours of nachos in a comforting bowl of soup! Roasted peppers, corn and onions swim in a rich, picante broth with softened lentils. A creamy dollop of guacamole and toasted chips finish off this one-pot dish!
